viewed', NULL, NULL, 'really good worked in a big company a bit expensive @ 70k \nhe stated that he can take a cut on the project \nand the only withdraw is that belal is actually much better at a.i but if belal is out this guy is in \n\nhe is aucian and he tried a filed entreprneue project', 4) ON CONFLICT (id) DO NOTHING;
